snippet.title: Divine Duel - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Get another look at Divine Duel in this launch trailer for the VR fighting game that mixes sci-fi and fantasy themes with crazy weaponry. Divine Duel will be available on Quest 2 AppLab on March 1, 2023.

In Divine Duel, step inside the arena and defeat your rivals using a combination of over 40 weapons, spells, and summons at your disposal.
